    "The most prominent topic, with ongoing branches, is antisemitism-hostility, prejudice, or discrimination against Jews [41].",
    "A closer look at the family is presented in Fig. 5.Government and Politics: This family has a large group with 30 branches, in which the discussions mainly revolve around political figures and events related to the American government.",
    "However, many discussions are based on information that lacks credible evidence.",
    "The two major topics of discussion in this group are the deaths of political figures Figure 5 Race and Religion familyand other celebrities, as well as rumors and conspiracies surrounding their deaths, and QAnon.",
    "The latter of these originated from anonymous posts by a user named 'Q' on Internet forums in 2017."
